# Deployment Configuration for Munir Demo Chat App

## Build Commands
# Web build: expo export --platform web
# Android build: expo build:android
# iOS build: expo build:ios

## Environment Variables (set these before building)
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=your-api-url
# EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_VERSION=1.0.0

## Platform-specific notes:
# Web: Built files will be in the 'dist' folder
# Android: APK will be available for download from Expo
# iOS: IPA will be available for download from Expo (requires Apple Developer account)

## Hosting recommendations:
# Web: Vercel, Netlify, or any static hosting service
# Mobile: Google Play Store, Apple App Store, or direct APK/IPA distribution